# ⚖️ AI-Based Case Posting & Lawyer Engagement System

A full-stack web application that connects clients with lawyers using AI-powered case classification and smart matching. This platform simplifies legal assistance by enabling users to post cases, find suitable lawyers, and manage legal interactions efficiently.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 🧠 AI-based case classification
* 👨‍⚖️ Lawyer discovery & engagement
* 📄 Case posting & management
* 💬 Real-time messaging system
* 📅 Appointment booking
* 💳 Secure payment integration
* 🔔 Notifications system
* 🛡️ Fraud detection module
* 📊 Admin dashboard & analytics

---

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**

* React.js (Vite)
* CSS

**Backend:**

* Node.js
* Express.js

**Database:**

* MongoDB

**Other Tools:**

* JWT Authentication
* REST APIs
* Socket.IO (Real-time communication)

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
├── backend/
│   ├── routes/
│   ├── services/
│   ├── utils/
│   └── server.js
│
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   ├── components/
│   ├── pages/
│   └── main.jsx
```

---

## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/dhanushkodi847-star/AI-Based-Case-Posting-and-Lawyer-Engaged-System.git
cd AI-Based-Case-Posting-and-Lawyer-Engaged-System
```

---

### 2️⃣ Install dependencies

#### Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

#### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
```

---

## 🔐 Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file inside the `backend` folder:

```
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
STRIPE_SECRET=your_stripe_key
```

---

## ▶️ Run the Project

### Start Backend

```bash
cd backend
npm run dev
```

### Start Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```

